<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>New Ticket Created: {{ticketTitle}}</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 style="color: #333;">New Ticket Created</h1>
    <h2 style="color: #007cba;">{{ticketTitle}}</h2>
    <p>A new ticket has been created in the project: <strong>{{projectName}}</strong></p>
    <div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0;">
      <p>{{ticketDescription}}</p>
    </div>
    <p>You can track the status of this ticket in the JasaWeb Client Portal.</p>
    <a href="{{ticketLink}}" style="background-color: #007cba; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 10px 0;">
      View Ticket
    </a>
    <br>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The JasaWeb Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>